profile:
Terminix Canada is one of the most respected professional pest control companies in the country, providing customer service from coast to coast for over 90 years. We specialize in residential, commercial and wildlife pest control solutions. This includes treatments for bedbugs, cockroaches, fleas, ticks, ants, termites, spiders, beetles, stinging insects, rats, mice, raccoons, skunks, birds and more.

Business Hours: Mon-Sun: Open 24 Hours

Address: 230 Hodgson Road, Fredericton, New Brunswick, E3C 2G4
